name: Night of 16th September / Morning of 17th September 2021
description:
I have dreams almost every day. If I'm asleep between the hours of 7:00am to 10:00am, I'm 100% guaranteed to experience a dream. This account to me is a dream journal I'll be updating with dreams I've had that I can recall or ones I wrote down lest I forgot.

As long as the blockchain is alive, they can never be destroyed.
